title: All in One SEO Pack 2.2.7.1 - WordPress Plugins
description:
All in One SEO Pack is a WordPress SEO plugin to automatically optimize your WordPress blog for Search Engines such as Google. All in One SEO Pack Optimizes your WordPress blog for SEO (Search Engine Optimization). Contains external links.

WP Requirements:
3.3 or higher, up to 4.2.4

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
